                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8920" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MSL-0113</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2153 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">谋“定”后“控”：数字赋能江苏大生集团内部控制进阶之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Planning for &quot;Determination&quot; and &quot;Control&quot;: The Road to Digital Empowerment of Jiangsu Dasheng Group&#39;s Internal Control Advancement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨锴，沈妍，杨涛，罗晓瑞，郭子荥，强文君，王思成，钱心茹</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京信息工程大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏大生集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">监察与纪检部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部控制；资源行动；风险管理；竞合战略；大生集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internal control; resource action; risk management; competitive strategy; Dasheng Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">尽管中国纺织业规模庞大、集中程度高，但是企业内部控制在风险管理领域缺乏超前理念、长期高度依赖绩效考核，严重制约纺织业高质量发展和绿色转型。在企业智能化改造、数字化转型背景下，本案例以江苏大生集团在2013年至2023年间集团内部控制探索过程为例，讲述了企业在三个探索过程中不断数字赋能和平台构建、逐步推进和持续优化、过程控制和效率提升的故事，提出了在智慧工厂建设过程中未来如何建设内部控制的问题。基于资源行动、风险管理和竞合战略等理论，本案例展现了江苏大生集团在资源行动方面从数字资源拼凑到内控资源协奏的转变，在风险管理方面从内控体系标准化到风险防控系统化的转变，在竞合战略方面从强化事中过程控制到数字赋能生产创新的转变。本案例揭示了中国纺织企业在数字化转型过程中资源行动、风险管理和竞合战略的共演规律，为传统纺织企业在智慧化转型实践提供启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Despite the large scale and high concentration of China&#39;s textile industry, the internal control of enterprises lacks advanced concepts in risk management and relies heavily on performance evaluation for a long time, seriously restricting the high-quality development and green transformation of the textile industry. In the context of enterprise intelligent transformation and digital transformation, this case takes Jiangsu Dasheng Group&#39;s internal control exploration process from 2013 to 2023 as an example, telling the story of the enterprise&#39;s continuous digital empowerment and platform construction, gradual promotion and continuous optimization, process control and efficiency improvement in three exploration processes. It proposes how to build internal control in the future during the construction of smart factories. Based on theories such as resource action, risk management, and competitive strategy, this case demonstrates the transformation of Jiangsu Dasheng Group from digital resource assembly to internal control resource coordination in resource action, from standardization of internal control system to systematization of risk prevention and control in risk management, and from strengthening in-process control to digital empowerment of production innovation in competitive strategy. This case reveals the co-evolution law of resource action, risk management, and competitive strategy in the digital transformation process of Chinese textile enterprises, providing inspiration for traditional textile enterprises in their intelligent transformation practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制与风险管理》、《内部控制理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部控制本质；内部控制风险；内部控制数字化转型路径</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
